	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Super Nintendo to mono TV</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Plug one of the two channels and set the game options to &quot;mono&quot;.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


